=== 农业在黎凡特的起源 ===
大约在10000-9000年前，农业首先出现在地处亚洲大陆西南部的[[黎凡特|黎凡特]]地区，该地区主要驯化了三种谷物：[[二粒小麦|二粒小麦]]、[[一粒小麦|一粒小麦]]和[[大麦|大麦]]，四种蔬菜：[[扁豆|扁豆]]、[[豌豆|豌豆]]、[[苦野豌豆|苦野豌豆]]和[[鹰嘴豆|鹰嘴豆]]，以及[[亚麻|亚麻]]。驯化的过程是缓慢的，可能花费了数百年，甚至上千年的时间。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The complex origins of domesticated crops in the Fertile Crescent|url=https://www.cell.com/trends/ecology-evolution/abstract/S0169-5347(08)00347-9|last=Brown|first=Terence A.|last2=Jones|first2=Martin K.|date=2009-02-01|journal=Trends in Ecology & Evolution|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.tree.2008.09.008|volume=24|pages=103–109|language=en|issn=0169-5347|pmid=19100651|last3=Powell|first3=Wayne|last4=Allaby|first4=Robin G.}}</ref>

在奥哈洛二号遗址（Ohalo II）发现的种子与研磨石的历史可以追溯到距今19400年前，这些发现或许表明，当时居住在奥哈洛附近的人们有意种植了一些植物以供食用，并且他们会对这些作为食物的种子做一些预处理。<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/54677732|publisher=Harvard University Press|date=2004|location=Cambridge, Mass.|isbn=0-674-01570-3|oclc=54677732|first=Steven J.|last=Mithen|title=After the ice : a global human history, 20,000-5000 BC}}</ref><ref>Compiled largely with reference to: Weiss, E., Mordechai, E., Simchoni, O., Nadel, D., & Tschauner, H. (2008). Plant-food preparation area on an Upper Paleolithic brush hut floor at Ohalo II, Israel. Journal of Archaeological Science, 35 (8), 2400–2414.</ref>泰尔·阿斯瓦德（Tell Aswad）是人们发现的最古老的农业遗址，其中驯化的二粒小麦可追溯到距今10800年前。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=AFLP Analysis of a Collection of Tetraploid Wheats Indicates the Origin of Emmer and Hard Wheat Domestication in Southeast Turkey|url=https://doi.org/10.1093/oxfordjournals.molbev.a004002|last=Özkan|first=H.|last2=Brandolini|first2=A.|date=2002-10-01|journal=Molecular Biology and Evolution|issue=10|doi=10.1093/oxfordjournals.molbev.a004002|volume=19|pages=1797–1801|issn=0737-4038|last3=Schäfer-Pregl|first3=R.|last4=Salamini|first4=F.}}</ref><ref>van Zeist, W. Bakker-Heeres, J.A.H., Archaeobotanical Studies in the Levant 1. Neolithic Sites in the Damascus Basin: Aswad, Ghoraifé, Ramad., Palaeohistoria, 24, 165–256, 1982.</ref>随后不久，在[[約旦河谷|约旦河谷]]的[[杰里科|杰里科]]和[[约旦|约旦]]的伊拉克埃德杜布（Iraq ed-Dubb）出现了带壳的二棱大麦。<ref>Hopf, Maria., "Jericho plant remains" in Kathleen M. Kenyon and T. A. Holland (eds.) Excavations at Jericho 5, pp. 576–621, British School of Archaeology at Jerusalem, London, 1983.</ref>黎凡特走廊上其他显示出早期农业证据的区域还包括瓦迪·费南16号遗址（Wadi Faynan 16）和内特夫·哈格杜德（Netiv Hagdud）遗址。Jacques Cauvin 指出，泰尔阿斯瓦德的定居者并不是在当地进行的驯化工作，而是“可能从邻近的东黎巴嫩山脉（Anti-Lebanon）引进了具备种植能力的种子”。<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/41645947|publisher=Cambridge University Press|date=2000|location=Cambridge, UK|isbn=0-521-65135-2|oclc=41645947|first=Trevor|last=Watkins|title=The birth of the Gods and the origins of agriculture|access-date=2022-02-12|archive-date=2022-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220523090417/http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/41645947}}</ref>在[[新月沃土|新月沃土]]东部，考古学家在位于伊朗的乔加戈兰（Choga Gholan）发现了野生植物的种植证据，其年代约为公元前12000年，这表明在大致同一时间，新月沃土中有多个地区同时出现了对植物的驯化行为。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Emergence of Agriculture in the Foothills of the Zagros Mountains of Iran|url=https://www.science.org/doi/abs/10.1126/science.1236743|last=Riehl|first=Simone|last2=Zeidi|first2=Mohsen|date=2013-07-05|journal=Science|doi=10.1126/science.1236743|language=EN|last3=Conard|first3=Nicholas J.|access-date=2022-02-12|archive-date=2022-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220212054615/https://www.science.org/doi/abs/10.1126/science.1236743}}</ref>考古学家在黎巴嫩[[约旦河|约旦河]]源附近的大约50个遗址中发现了包含有重石器（Heavy Neolithic）的卡劳恩文化（Qaraoun culture ），但尚未确定其具体年代。<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=|url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=6mKBAAAAMAAJ&redir_esc=y|publisher=Oxbow Books|date=2004|isbn=978-1-84217-132-5|language=en|first=E. J.|last=Peltenburg|first2=Alexander|last2=Wasse|title=Neolithic Revolution: New Perspectives on Southwest Asia in Light of Recent Discoveries on Cyprus|access-date=2022-02-12|archive-date=2022-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220212054648/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=6mKBAAAAMAAJ&redir_esc=y}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|chapter=|url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=qhPRQwAACAAJ&redir_esc=y|publisher=éditeur non identifié|date=1966|language=en|first=Lorraine|last=Copeland|title=Inventory of Stone Age Sites in Lebanon: North, South and East-Central Lebanon. Part two|access-date=2022-02-12|archive-date=2022-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220212060403/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=qhPRQwAACAAJ&redir_esc=y}}</ref>

=== 东亚 ===
中国在新石器时代的农业发展可以大致划分为两大区域：华南与华北。<ref name=":3">{{Cite journal|title=Prehistoric evolution of the dualistic structure mixed rice and millet farming in China|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/317400332_Prehistoric_evolution_of_the_dualistic_structure_mixed_rice_and_millet_farming_in_China|last=He|first=Keyang|last2=Lu|first2=Houyuan|date=2017-06-07|journal=The Holocene|doi=10.1177/0959683617708455|volume=27|pages=1885–1898|last3=Zhang|first3=Jianping|last4=Wang|first4=Can|last5=Huan|first5=Xiujia|access-date=2022-02-12|archive-date=2022-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220214235110/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/317400332_Prehistoric_evolution_of_the_dualistic_structure_mixed_rice_and_millet_farming_in_China}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite journal|title=The Checkered Prehistory of Rice Movement Southwards as a Domesticated Cereal—from the Yangzi to the Equator|url=https://thericejournal.springeropen.com/articles/10.1007/s12284-011-9068-9|last=Bellwood|first=Peter|date=2011-12|journal=Rice|issue=3|doi=10.1007/s12284-011-9068-9|volume=4|pages=93–103|language=en|issn=1939-8433|access-date=2022-02-12|archive-date=2022-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220307191851/https://thericejournal.springeropen.com/articles/10.1007/s12284-011-9068-9}}</ref>
