中国华北的农业中心可能位于早期[[汉藏语系|汉藏语系]]的人口聚居地，以及包括[[黄河|黄河盆地]]中的[[后李文化|后李文化]]、[[裴李崗文化|裴李岗文化]]、[[磁山文化|磁山文化]]和[[兴隆洼文化|兴隆洼文化]]。<ref name=":3" /><ref name=":4" />居住在这个区域的人类在距今大约8000年前驯化了[[小米|小米]]和[[高粱|高粱]]<ref name="#3">{{Cite journal|title=Contrasting Patterns in Crop Domestication and Domestication Rates: Recent Archaeobotanical Insights from the Old World|url=https://doi.org/10.1093/aob/mcm048|last=Fuller|first=Dorian Q.|date=2007-10-01|journal=Annals of Botany|issue=5|doi=10.1093/aob/mcm048|volume=100|pages=903–924|issn=0305-7364|pmc=PMC2759199|pmid=17495986}}</ref>，并从距今7500年前开始广泛种植。<ref name="#3"/>[[大豆|大豆]]也是在华北驯化的，驯化时间大约在距今4500年前。<ref>Siddiqi, Mohammad Rafiq (2001). ''Tylenchida: Parasites of Plants and Insects''. CABI.</ref>橙子和桃子也起源于中国，它们在公元前2500年左右开始种植。<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/5133474|publisher=University of California Press|date=1979|location=Berkeley|isbn=0-520-03736-7|oclc=5133474|first=Christopher|last=Thacker|title=The history of gardens}}</ref><ref>Webber, Herbert John (1967–1989). Chapter I. [http://websites.lib.ucr.edu/agnic/webber/Vol1/Chapter1.htm History and Development of the Citrus Industry Archived] {{Webarchive|url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20160523072403/http://websites.lib.ucr.edu/agnic/webber/Vol1/Chapter1.htm |date=2016-05-23 }} 2016-05-23 at the Portuguese Web Archive in ''Origin of Citrus'', Vol. 1. University of California</ref>

中国华南的农业中心位于[[长江|长江流域]]附近。距今大约13500-8200年前，该区域居民驯化了[[水稻|水稻]]，并发展出了使用[[稻田|稻田]]的种植方式。<ref name="#2"/><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Molecular evidence for a single evolutionary origin of domesticated rice|url=https://www.pnas.org/content/108/20/8351|last=Molina|first=Jeanmaire|last2=Sikora|first2=Martin|date=2011-05-17|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=20|doi=10.1073/pnas.1104686108|volume=108|pages=8351–8356|language=en|issn=0027-8424|pmid=21536870|last3=Garud|first3=Nandita|last4=Flowers|first4=Jonathan M.|last5=Rubinstein|first5=Samara|last6=Reynolds|first6=Andy|last7=Huang|first7=Pu|last8=Jackson|first8=Scott|last9=Schaal|first9=Barbara A.|access-date=2022-02-12|archive-date=2022-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123224339/https://www.pnas.org/content/108/20/8351}}</ref><ref name=":5">{{Cite journal|title=Early Mixed Farming of Millet and Rice 7800 Years Ago in the Middle Yellow River Region, China|url=https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0052146|last=Zhang|first=Jianping|last2=Lu|first2=Houyuan|date=2012-12-17|journal=PLOS ONE|issue=12|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0052146|volume=7|pages=e52146|language=en|issn=1932-6203|pmc=PMC3524165|pmid=23284907|last3=Gu|first3=Wanfa|last4=Wu|first4=Naiqin|last5=Zhou|first5=Kunshu|last6=Hu|first6=Yayi|last7=Xin|first7=Yingjun|last8=Wang|first8=Can|access-date=2022-06-28|archive-date=2022-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220507233049/https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0052146}}</ref>
